title: Maid in Akihabara (4 of 6) Japanese Drama [iichan]
description:
Maid in Akihabara is a 6 episode series that was produced in Japan on 2005 and released on February 24, 2006. Each episode ran about 15 minutes, and took place in Akihabara, Tokyo - the cyber city of Japan. The story begins when a woman, named Saki, tries to find a job to hide from a bar gang, since she had worked at a bar before. She ends up getting a job at a Maid cafe called Meido no miyage (Maid&#039;s gift). She is the third maid to be joining the cafe. She is homeless and lives in a 24-hour internet cafe.
